We also take a computational approach to the assembly of the Boolean query. A naïve approach could involve trying all combinations of terms in a category with all combinations of all other terms in all other categories (similar to the manual trial-and-error employed in the original method). The complexity of this approach, however, presents itself as infeasible: \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
