We further propose to tune the term cut-off thresholds parameters for the filtering steps. Rather than fixing the thresholds at 20% for development and 2% for population (as done by Hausner et al. [4]), we perform a grid search (independently for each query) over combinations of thresholds to find the parameters best suited (optimising for \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
